snippet.title: Sucker Punch VR  Steam Beta Trailer #1
snippet.description:
Sucker Punch VR is an immersive single and multiplayer experience! Battle your opponents in a variety of diverse arenas using an arsenal of power-ups! Punch point cubes as they come at you to send them flying back at your opponent. As you battle, and your power-meter charges, unleash power-ups to overwhelm your opposition and defend your goal!

Coming soon to Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1491400/Sucker_Punch/
